full_summary:
# **Mixed Boat Trailers Tender**

## **Title**
##### English: Boat Trailers Mixed
##### French: Remorques à Bateaux Mixtes

## **Reference**
#### Reference Number: PW-22-01007038
#### Solicitation Number: W8476-236612/A

## **Call for Proposals**

The Department of National Defence is issuing a call for proposals under the [Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA), Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement, Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA), Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement, Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement, Canada-Ukraine Free Trade Agreement (CUFTA), and World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO GPA)].

The procurement is for [Qty 18] x Boat Trailers Mixed and their respective ILS deliverables. Key delivery locations include various sites across Canada, with a requested delivery date of 120 days from Contract Award.

## **Contact Information**

For further information, please contact:

Grundy, Kyle
DLP 5-3-6
kyle.grundy@forces.gc.ca
101 Colonel By Dr, Ottawa, Ontario, K1A0K2, Canada

## **Proposals Deadlines**

*   Publication Date: 2022-09-13
*   Tender Closing Date: 2022-10-04T14:00:00

## **Contracting Entity Details**

*   Contracting Entity: Department of National Defence
*   Address: 101 Colonel By Dr, Ottawa, Ontario, K1A0K2, Canada

Please visit [https://canadabuys.canada.ca/documents/pub/att/2022/09/13/db84aa90f2a7292221393d7323761ba0/rfp_w8476-236612_bt304.pdf](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/documents/pub/att/2022/09/13/db84aa90f2a7292221393d7323761ba0/rfp_w8476-236612_bt304.pdf) for the tender documents.

[End of Tender Announcement.]
